align=left class=m><span class=title> Incredible Wis Item</span><hr size=1> Anyone had a chance to get an Othmir Prexus Totem yet?  Stats are AC 5  Sta 20  Wis 18  Cha Neg 8.  Plus it is range equippable.  <br>
<br>
<br>
For those who do not know this item is obtained through a quest and is incredibly easy to complete.  You need to kill the Sea dragon in CS to get the sea dragon meat.  Other things you need to do is go fishing in OOT and Karanas....  I had a zero fishing skill before I started the quest and when I got the last piece I needed my fishing skill was at 43.<br>
<br>
I believe this is a definite must have item as it is range slot equippable and would free up other slots for AC, mana, resists or other things which anyone may like better.  That coupled with the Epic and a quest BP can use the rest of your slots for other types of gear.<br>
<br>
Last thought.... Anyone know what the price is for an item like this?  Not that anyone would truly want to sell, but.....  one never knows if one may be in a position to build another twink....<br>
<br>
Eannyil<br>
